title: LinkedIn Cuts 668 Jobs in Second Layoff Round This Year
description: The 3 percent reduction in the company’s global work force follows 716 layoffs in May.

title: Top FTX Executive Says Sam Bankman-Fried Used Customer Money for ‘Excess’ Spending
description: Nishad Singh, testifying at Mr. Bankman-Fried’s fraud trial, said FTX customer deposits were used to buy luxury real estate and to pay athletes like Tom Brady and Steph Curry for endorsement deals.

title: How ‘A.I. Agents’ That Roam the Internet Could One Day Replace Workers
description: Researchers are transforming chatbots into online agents that play games, query websites, schedule meetings, build bar charts and do more.
